  "stem": "<p>The function <i>g</i> is defined by <i>g</i>(<i>x</i>) = (1/8)<i>x</i> &minus; 5. What is the <i>y</i>-intercept of the graph of <i>y</i> = <i>g</i>(<i>x</i>) in the <i>xy</i>-plane?</p>",
