  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. The <i>y</i>-intercept is the point where <i>x</i> = 0: <i>g</i>(0) = &minus;5, so the <i>y</i>-intercept is (0, &minus;5).</p><p>Choice B swaps coordinates. Choices C and D use the slope value.</p>",
